name: Jet Cat (Version 1.5)
description:
This is the new version of the Game Jet Cat the previous version was a completed disaster, most of the code wasn't optimized. So that makes the the game more slow and also on different platforms the game cound not start bad starting

A curious cat wants to fly freely in the sky !!! Our Cat can fly at high speed with a power jet-pack, but controls are not easy. We must be careful as there are many birds that could ruin our exciting journey. Would you help this kitten ?

This is a very simple game, I hope you like it.
